### 测试地址管理API

### 1. 获取地址列表 (需要先登录获取token)
GET http://localhost:18080/api/users/me/addresses
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. 创建地址
POST http://localhost:18080/api/users/me/addresses
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiverName": "张三",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "province": "上海市",
  "city": "上海市",
  "district": "浦东新区",
  "detailAddress": "张江高科技园区XXX路123号",
  "postalCode": "200000",
  "isDefault": true
}

### 3. 获取用户信息验证token是否有效
GET http://localhost:18080/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE